Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The book-selling business
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w54f
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Oct 1980
How the book-selling business creates a bestseller from a book which isn't selling. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.